from pyspark.ml.feature import HashingTF
from pyspark.ml.feature import CountVectorizer

cv = CountVectorizer(inputCol = "words", outputCol = "tf")
model = cv.fit(df_filter)
tf = model.transform(df_filter)

tf.show()

%pyspark

from pyspark.ml.feature import IDF

idf = IDF(inputCol = "tf", outputCol = "tf*idf")

tfidf = idf.fit(tf).transform(tf)
tfidf.show()
%pyspark

import pywsd
from pywsd import disambiguate
from pywsd.similarity import max_similarity as maxsim

df_filter2 = (df.rdd.map(lambda r : (r.id, nltk.pos_tag(nltk.word_tokenize(' '.join(r.words)))))).toDF().withColumnRenamed("_1", "doc_id").withColumnRenamed("_2", "words")

print df_filter2.count()
df_filter2.take(100)
